description:
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a motivated individual to join our Out of Hours Community Nursing Service which delivers highly skilled care to patients in their own homes. If you are conscientious, enthusiastic, forward thinking and are looking for a change of direction we welcome enquiries from you. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Out of Hours District Nursing Service is part of the 24 hour District Nursing Service. Hours of work for this part of the District Nursing Service are between 8pm – 8am. Full training and an individual induction will be provided to the successful candidate. P.C.I.C. is committed to supporting its staff and promoting new and interesting ways of providing care for patients in the Community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 08/11/2020 &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact: &lt;/p&gt;
